text: Rafael Lucena Marques (born 11 September 1989) is a Portuguese football player who plays for Oriental. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Segunda Liga for Oriental on 20 September 2015 in a game against Desportivo Aves. ==References== ==External links== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:C.D.
